snippet.title: Grandia III ~ Opening (1920x1080)
snippet.description:
Extracted from the original ENG PS2 DVD game and upscaled using Celestial Being UHD Encoding Software v3.6 and Cell Enhancement plugin developed by Celestial Being RAW Providing Group.

Upscaled from 512x288 to 1920x1080.

Copyright Info:

Developer(s)  Game Arts
Publisher(s)  Square Enix
Composer(s)  Noriyuki Iwadare
Platform(s)  PlayStation 2
Release date(s)  
    JP August 4, 2005
    NA February 14, 2006

Genre(s)  Console role-playing game
Mode(s)  Single-player
Rating(s)  
    CERO: B (Ages 12 and up)
    ESRB: T (Teen)

Media/distribution  2 DVDs

Copyright belongs to SquareEnix for the game Grandia III and In the Sky is performed by MIZ, published by Victor Entertainment on August 3, 2005 in the albums IN THE SKY (Game "Grandia III" Main Theme) [Limited Edition] with the catalog number VIZL-144 and IN THE SKY [Regular Edition] with the catalog number VICL-35861.
